sources.title: TWO (Do) By Soheila GOLESTANI
sources.description: TWO (Do) By Soheila GOLESTANI Synopsis TWO is the story of a femme de chamber ( 40 years old ) who is hire to help Bahman who comes back to Iran to sell his father’s house in packing the furniture and equipment, this collaboration change their destiny but not in a good way … ****** Cast: Mahtab Nasirpour, Parviz Parastui, Mohammad Rabbani, Mohammadreza Sajadi, Mehraneh MahinTorabi, Sogol Khaligh, Mostafa Zand, Sara Garachedaghi, Esmaeil Gorgi
